    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed the required gradation level for Model Risk Level 2. Six factors are appropriately scoped out at MRL 2. The CFD model demonstrates adequate credibility to support identification of worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device. The relative hemolysis index predictions are within acceptable uncertainty bounds relative to experimental measurements and the RH < 1 acceptance criterion is satisfied.",
